items.headline: Fighterpedia! The Ultimate Fighting Resource
items.desc: Ever wanted to know about all your favorite fighting characters and games? Well, visit Fighterpedia! From Street Fighter to King of Fighters, this is the ultimate resource for everything about Fighting! Even character strategies and movelists! Along with TONS of special content and activities that'll make you have a great time!
